==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From [[βαπτίζω]] {{GG|907}}; a [[baptizer]], as an epithet of Christ’s forerunner: 

===Pronunciation===
*Βαπτιστής / Baptistēs / bap-tis-tace'

===Proper noun===
'''Βαπτιστής'''

# [[Baptist]].

